Package: shm
Type: Package
Version: 0.1
Author: Mohamed Uduman, Gur Yaari, Namita Gupta
Maintainer: Mohamed Uduman <mohamed.uduman@yale.edu>
Title: Somatic Hypermutation Analysis
Description: A new computational framework for Bayesian estimation of
    Antigen-driven selection in Immunoglobulin sequences, provides a more
    intuitive means of analyzing selection by actually quantifying it. Along
    with advanced analysis of SHM in Ig sequences.
License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0
URL: http://clip.med.yale.edu/changeo
